                        <p>Competitive prices to fit your budget.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li style="margin-top: 20px;" >
                        <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
                        <h4  >Excellence</h4>
                        <p>Striving to exceed your expectations in every interaction.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li style="margin-top: 20px;" >
                        <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                        <h4 >Sustainability</h4>
                        <p>We're committed to responsible practices for a better environment.</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
